Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.00,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}翻译：傻瓜三世 ZERO 逆火 校对：傻瓜三世\N\N后期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老师 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小渊泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我奶奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 你赶快回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我奶奶怎麽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切彷彿像作梦一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 为什麽醒不来呢 怎麽都醒不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梦好像永远都不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 我依然在这个梦中
