Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:57.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪中黑\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&HB89E7E&\pos(660,625)}#致亲爱的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三星期？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不算远 但那裡不能搭直升机过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要坐雪地车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶 终于能坐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是值得开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雪地车很慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要避开冰缝等危险地带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能一下走这边 一下又换个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没不小心 是故意这麽剪的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫌头髮太长很烦的是小吟你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正比贵子剪的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要怎麽办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是可以 才请你一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以…花点时间考虑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为她会喊著「要去！」就扑过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个臭氧层破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这裡负责观测的队员发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并率先报告给全世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种观测会使用这种高层气象观测气球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天两次在世界各地同时释放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}3 2 1 释放气球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她想一个人想些事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队长跟她聊过后 她就不怎麽说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在这个点上与她失去了联繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs35\1c&HD2CAC3&\pos(412,154)\frz40.5}收件者：{\1c&HA29F93&}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs35\1c&HC3C0B4&\frz40.5\pos(596,256)}主旨：{\1c&H797B76&}致亲爱的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.30,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs35\1c&H414945&\pos(386,686)\frz42.81}来自我的myPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山顶茶屋复活啦 有啤酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经冰镇好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真机灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什麽 觉得拍摄结束了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天真暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在可是盛夏 今天算冷的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才放气球了 你在这裡看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的点心好像是红豆麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 没什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是 那个怎麽说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H7B8084&\frz358.5\pos(640,106)}今天的菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H8177D9&\frz23.28\pos(410,70)}特别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H868D8C&\pos(820,142)}DE送行会！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H666765&\frz2.782\pos(514,464)}蔬菜也要好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H666765&\pos(914,438)\frz5.631}还有啤酒喝{\i1}！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你问我妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理做事太没计划 才搞得这麽複杂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麽想到主动请缨问报濑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没有消沉和烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是觉得普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点普通过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直觉得自己来了南极会大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「这就是妈妈看过的景色啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「妈妈是感动于这片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得这裡很美 所以她才想来一趟的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我幻想自己会这样感叹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但实际上完全不是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至觉得一切都跟照片上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得刚到的时候 你第一句话就是「活该」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你是因为妈妈在等你才来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为妈妈来过 才想说自己也要来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才不断拜託佳苗小姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还打工赚钱 费尽心思就想来这裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑你说过的 妈妈在这裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这样说 报濑就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己是为了什麽来到这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是到那裡后就是尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果到了那裡 依然没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一辈子都会是现在的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在远征大陆前 我想为南极挑战及民间南极观测
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发表30分钟左右的演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啤酒要结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开个玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想说的只有简单的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要出发了 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不快点吃 很快就会变成冷肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.58,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是南极烧烤最有趣的一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}棉花糖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你凑太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我听说小渊泽还在犹豫去不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们真就不管她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多管閒事不是体贴人 有时不管也是种体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又乱编名言了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我们大致得出的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真羡慕你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能给彼此空间 说明你们感情很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什麽鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说我们是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是好朋友啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不去吃烧烤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也知道我不喜欢太热闹的场合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是怎麽想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麽事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我妈妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种问题都要问我的话 那我劝你别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论你有多麽不愿意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子去世的事实也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我们说是继承她的遗志 生前的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但没人知道 这是否是她的真心想法与愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那为什麽又要来南极一趟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我想来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我自私地认为 贵子希望我这麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说到底 人只会为自己的信念而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但只有信念 才能让人在现实中披荆斩棘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}化不可能为可能 推动自己前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是说 我不该顺著别人的想法做事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不就是这麽走过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搬家工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清扫工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清扫工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}送报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道自己是在强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搬家工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交通量调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清扫工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快递
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我无论如何都想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:10.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Bold\bord0\fs45\1c&H8C85D2&\frz8.085\frx356\fry346\pos(316,458)}加油{\fsp-15}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:10.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic Bold\bord0\fs65\1c&HA98CCE&\frx356\fry346\frz351\move(378,112,188,-72,0,633)}加油{\fsp-15}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吧 这可是手工的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说内陆之旅也要带著这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是你的行李？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太多了 减半 五分钟搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样 最后的旅途开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝著距离日本14,000公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比宇宙更遥远 恍若天边的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来不是坐雪地车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个S-16是我们内陆之旅的起始据点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给停靠此地的雪地车装货就是今天的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡比昭和基地要冷多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡看到的景色 就很有南极的味道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人有7对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}7对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然连续三轮当大贫民…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡是114 通过S-18
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 112收到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要到外面去 做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛 每吸一口气胸口就好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻子都快没感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来随著海拔提高 还会更冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还真带来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没知觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不快吃就冷掉萝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上会把引擎关掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃料可没多到能一直开著引擎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡是昭和 这裡是昭和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}内陆组能听到吗 请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定时联络 来练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我们都不知道接下来会发生什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚风势可能会增强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在车辆间移动一定要抓紧这条绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算只有几公尺也不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是被暴风雪卷走 就回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是太阳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点像世界末日到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那叫太阳光柱 也就是Sun Pillar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是由冰晶反射产生的光学现象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也看到过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 她看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以说她站在那裡 看著看著就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道是暴风雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是暴风雪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题的 只要待在车裡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麽都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对喔 你们还是第一次亲眼见到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈失踪的时候也是这种情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许是东西忘在内陆基地裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也可能是滑了一跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我发现的时候 她已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没过多久 暴风雪就颳了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睡不著吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 刚刚才睡醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理喜欢南极吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果是一个人来 就不知道喜不喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要大家一起 去北极或许也会一样喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你带我来这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你帮我找到了自己的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}致亲爱的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直喜欢当独行侠的我交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然她们有点怪 有点麻烦 还有点废
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但却是陪著我走到了南极的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们吵过架 流过泪 也出过问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们依旧走过长长的旅途 来到了妈妈到过的这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为和大家一起 我才走到了这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 从你那边能看到什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也能看到 你看过的风景吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很快就会到妈妈在的那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:14.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康超特楷体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H353749&\frz2.986\move(718,8,718,262,37,4166)}南极挑战第一次派遣队天文观测站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让你久等了 虽然还得让你等一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:31.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康超特楷体\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H353749&\frz10.31\move(546,188,546,496,0,7753)}南极挑战第一次派遣队天文观测站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来要重新打地基 盖房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把零件一个个运来 製造望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然建立小渊泽天文台还要不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小渊泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她肯定是回想起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我妈妈一起看这裡时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能找到妈妈的东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都三年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 换个角度想 这裡有三年没人来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了啦 不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能轻言放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麽都行 哪怕就一样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什麽你能这麽断定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能到这裡就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经完成目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经到过妈妈在的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你们 所以已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以 我们都到这裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都到这裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个也好 我们要找到报濑妈妈来过这裡的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:34.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}そっ之「会いたい」闻いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:42.51,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}空に溶けて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:21:00.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今も胸の奥　静かに揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:07.91,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}白く辉く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:16.20,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}残した足迹も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:24.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}果てない之思ってた时が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:32.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}终わりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:42.44,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だからずっ之忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:51.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}言叶より大切な思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:22:01.15,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}きっ之繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:13.13,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつの日か　また旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:54.30,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}だからずっ之忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:03.98,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}一绪にいた　かけがえのない时が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:13.21,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}きっ之繋いでくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:24.89,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}いつまでも　いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:30.21,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40\an3}またね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:34.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}听见一声轻轻的「想见你」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:42.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}声音渐渐消失在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:21:00.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我的心底依然在暗自动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:07.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}雪白闪耀的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:16.20,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我们踩下的足迹 渐渐褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:24.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}原以为这些时光 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:32.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却突然画上了句号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:42.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以这份心情 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:51.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}它比任何语言 都要宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:22:01.15,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}总有一天 会再度牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:13.13,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}带著我们 又一次踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:54.30,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}所以这些时光 我不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:03.98,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}你我一道 度过的珍贵点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:13.21,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}想必它们 会永远牵起你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:24.89,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}直到永远 直到永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:30.21,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\fs40}再见了
